---
title: Tilapia & Almond Parsley Gremolata with Carrots & Garlic Herb Couscous
description: Fishing for a delicious, sea-faring meal? We’ve got just the thing. Flaky tilapia fillets are rubbed with a bold seasoning blend, then roasted to perfection. Once they emerge from the oven, they’re drizzled with a bright Italian chopped herb sauce called gremolata combining fresh parsley, crunchy toasted almonds, garlic, lemon, and olive oil. On the side, there’s roasted carrots and buttery Israeli couscous. Yeah, that’s a whole ’lata weeknight goodness.
